      <li><strong>Knowledge of local requirements</strong> — We understand HOA rules and county codes</li>
      <li><strong>Established supplier relationships</strong> — Access to the best materials at competitive prices</li>
      <li><strong>Accountability</strong> — We're part of this community and our reputation matters</li>
    </ul>

